---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Research Documents | Complete Health Peptides"
  description="Access scientific research documents, certificates of analysis, and technical data sheets for our peptide products."
>
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-secondary-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Research Documents</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl">Access scientific documentation and resources for your research needs.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="mb-8">Our comprehensive research documentation is available in our documentation center. Please click the button below to access all research materials.</p>
          
          <div class="flex justify-center my-8">
            <a 
              href="https://docs.chpeptides.com/research" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer" 
              class="bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-medium text-lg transition inline-flex items-center"
            >
              Access Research Documents
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <h2>Available Research Materials</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Certificates of Analysis</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">Access certificates of analysis for all our research compounds, verifying purity and composition.</p>
              <a href="https://docs.chpeptides.com/research/certificates" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium inline-flex items-center">
                View Certificates
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Safety Data Sheets</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">Download safety data sheets containing handling, storage, and precautionary information.</p>
              <a href="https://docs.chpeptides.com/research/sds" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium inline-flex items-center">
                View SDS
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Technical Guides</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">Technical guides for laboratory handling, reconstitution, and storage of research compounds.</p>
              <a href="https://docs.chpeptides.com/research/guides" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium inline-flex items-center">
                View Guides
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Research Publications</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">References to scientific literature and research publications related to our products.</p>
              <a href="https://docs.chpeptides.com/research/publications" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium inline-flex items-center">
                View Publications
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 my-8">
            <p class="text-yellow-700"><strong>Note:</strong> All research materials are provided for informational purposes only. These documents are intended for researchers and laboratory professionals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>